          <h2>Directions</h2>
          <h3>How to get to Sehome Hill From I-5:</h3>
          <ol>
            <li>
              Take the Samish Way exit (Exit 252) to Bill MacDonald Parkway.
            </li>
            <li>
              Continue up Bill McDonald Parkway until you reach the edge of
              Western Washington University.
            </li>
            <li>
              Turn right on the road just before Buchanan Towers (across from
              the Washington Archive Building at 26th).
            </li>
            <li>
              From this point, you may continue up to the top of Sehome Hill and park, or park at the base of Sehome Hill and use the trails to navigate the Arboretum.
            </li>
          </ol>

